textBox.richText: I deem this summer The Summer of Breakups and/or Failed Relationships. I have gained knowledge of a total of five thus far. Wonder if that number will keep on climbin’!? </very dry scorn> But seriously, what the fuck? … On the bright side though, I think I’ve finally decided on now sticking with this change to a Biology major! Although who knows. I may doubt myself and have second (and third. And fourth.) thoughts about this yet again!
